snippet.title: Warhammer Age of Sigmar: Realms of Ruin - Official Release Date Trailer | gamescom 2023
snippet.description:
Warhammer Age of Sigmar: Realms of Ruin will be available on PC via Steam and the Epic Games Store, PlayStation 5, and Xbox Series X/S. Watch the latest trailer to meet the real-time strategy game's third faction, the spectral horde of the Nighthaunt, and check out the game's conquest mode--a repeatable single-player challenge mode.

#gamescom
